OL,3,CTwo-day dispersal order issued for
OL,4,CSwansea city centre
OL,6,FA two day dispersal order has been
OL,7,Fissued for parts of Swansea city
OL,8,Fcentre to help deal with anti-social
OL,9,Fbehaviour.
OL,11,FThe dispersal order came into effect
OL,12,Fon the evening of 30 May and it is due
OL,13,Fto expire on 1 June. It covers parts
OL,14,Fof the the city centre including a
OL,15,Fsection of The Kingsway, part of
OL,16,FOystermouth Road, and Quadrant
OL,17,FShopping Centre.
