OL,3,CTwo-day dispersal order issued for
OL,4,CSwansea city centre
OL,6,FUnder Section 35 of the Anti-Social
OL,7,FBehaviour Crime and Policing Act 2014,
OL,8,Fpolice officers can direct anyone who
OL,9,Fis causing, or is likely to cause,
OL,10,Fharassment, alarm, or distress to
OL,11,Fleave the specified area.
OL,13,FThe action has been taken to curb anti-
OL,14,Fsocial behaviour involving young
OL,15,Fpeople aged 10-17.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
