OL,3,CTwo-day dispersal order issued for
OL,4,CSwansea city centre
OL,6,FPolice Sergeant Molly Llewellyn
OL,7,Fstated: "We do not tolerate anti-
OL,8,Fsocial behaviour. Our officers will
OL,9,Fhave an increased presence in the
OL,10,Farea, and they won't hesitate to
OL,11,Futilise the powers granted to them to
OL,12,Fensure the safety of our community.
OL,14,F"We encourage parents and guardians to
OL,15,Ftalk to those they care for, urging
OL,16,Fthem to steer clear of any involvement
OL,17,Fin anti-social activities."
